name: test full Employee cancelation with MealPeriod and TravelTime
fullName: /SchedulingOptimizationRegression/Provider Cancellation & Non-Billable Events Optimisation#test full Employee cancelation with MealPeriod and TravelTime
descriptionHtml:
This endpoint retrieves the events for a specific draft schedule identified by the provided cancelOptimizationJobId, within the specified time range.

### Request

- Method: GET

- URL: `https://{{url}}/scheduling/draft-schedules/{{cancelOptimizationJobId}}/events`

- Query Parameters:
- start (string): The start date for the time range in ISO 8601 format.

- end (string): The end date for the time range in ISO 8601 format.


### Response

The response for this request will be in JSON format. Here is a JSON schema representing the response:

``` json
{
"type": "object",
"properties": {
"event1": {
"type": "object",
"properties": {
// Properties of event1
}
},
"event2": {
"type": "object",
"properties": {
// Properties of event2
}
},
// Additional events...
}
}

```
